column2: A small pier has been constructed to accommodate the emergence of a small fishing village. Some fish are caught here, but the waters are still teeming with wildlife and could yield even more were there more infrastructure to support local fishing.
column3: Un ponton a été construit afin d'y accueillir quelques barques de pêcheurs.

column2: The pier has been renovated into a quay capable of accommodating a sizeable flotilla of small fishing craft. The yield has increased considerably and can easily feed the local populace and leave a surplus for the salting and smoking industries
column3: Le ponton a été transformé en un quai et peut maintenant accueillir une flottille de pêche ramenant suffisamment de poissons tant pour nourrir la population locale qu'alimenter les activités de salage et fumage de la région.

column2: The quay has been expanded into a bustling harbor and the fishing industry is booming here.
column3: C'est maintenant un port fourmillant d'activités et accueillant une pêche abondante qui est installé sur le site.
